info:
$50 VISA GIFT CARD FOR WA RESIDENTS RECEIVING THEIR 1ST OR 2ND DOSES OF THE VACCINE***All WA residents receiving the vaccine at this clinic will receive a $50 Visa gift card that can be used anywhere Visa is accepted.*** You will need to agree we can collect your name and # at the clinic verifying you received the gift card.

The clinic is at N. Pines Middle School located at 11900 E. Broadway,  Spokane WA 99206.

 ***Residents of ANY state are now eligible for the vaccine, but you still must have photo ID*** 

 ***VERY IMPORTANT***Please complete all the insurance/Medicare/Medicaid information when registering online for your appointment to avoid filling it out at the clinic***
